        (<a> :href "http://www.java.com" "Java")
        )

   (<p> "Adder is a Lisp-1 which compiles to Python.  It aims to
integrate seamlessly into Python: every Adder function is a Python
function, every Adder list is a Python list, etc.
")

   (<p> "Python-on-Lisp has been tried before; I think Adder has two advantages
